high_descs: Move to the dining table to the left of you
Pick up a tomato from the table
Move to the microwave behind you
Heat the tomato in the microwave
Move to the fridge to the right of the table
Put the tomato inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, turn right and then right again to face the black table.
Pick up the tomato from the right side of the table.
Take the tomato and turn around to go to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and turn it on. Take the tomato out and shut the door.
Hold the tomato and turn around. Then turn right to face the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge then shut the door.
Turn around and walk around the table.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn around and take the tomato to the microwave.
Open the microwave and heat the tomato, then take it out.
Turn around and walk to the fridge with the tomato.
Put the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the tomato and put it in the fridge.
